果想掛石屎牆首先要用油壓鑽鑽牆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e1D4BzC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe1D4BzC.jpg&h=74298eff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個洞要鑽幾大請參考(<a href=\"http://www.moonskyedu.com/furniture/%E6%9C%A8%E5%B7%A5/03%E9%85%8D%E4%BB%B6%E8%88%87%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.moonskyedu.com%2Ffurniture%2F%25E6%259C%25A8%25E5%25B7%25A5%2F03%25E9%2585%258D%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%259D%2590%25E6%2596%2599.htm&d=r3KAKVFNaHluzyQg9s7QtgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=4d107cfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.moonskyedu.com/furniture/%E6%9C%A8%E5%B7%A5/03%E9%85%8D%E4%BB%B6%E8%88%87%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99.htm</a>)<br />\n然後要買膠塞用鎚仔打入個洞到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kVWNznw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkVWNznw.jpg&h=20b6be34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟住先鑽螺絲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KmhMPV1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKmhMPV1.jpg&h=d05961ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但一般螺絲批有機會唔夠力，e個時候就要用大馬力電鑽or e種鑽螺絲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dnCH7Jo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdnCH7Jo.jpg&h=d7f45d61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rwsXWBL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrwsXWBL.jpg&h=dd0fb79b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d22ec52f39cf64428a432a8ec6d0b5f127125301","tid":867201,"uid":139070,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:47:04.000Z","msg":"邊夠力，痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a393124bbcee4b4875016ddc9dc3551fa14603c","tid":867201,"uid":14792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70c583074f4210fddb5120f2b44b140cfb3a48e2","tid":867201,"uid":28181,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:21:49.000Z","msg":"如果想掛石屎牆首先要用油壓鑽鑽牆<br />\n<img src=\"ht